    UI -->|writes feedback entries| FB

    T -->|validates logic and reliability| GL
    CI -->|runs test suite| T

    HE -->|reviews logs and feedback| EL
    HE -->|reviews logs and feedback| FB
    HE -->|manual UI testing| UI